#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn4.14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.14:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.14:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. Rule "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Patirūpasutta "
msgstr "14. Appropriate "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn4.14:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu viharati ekasālāyaṃ brāhmaṇagāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Kosalans near the brahmin village of Ekasālā. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.14:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā mahatiyā gihiparisāya parivuto dhammaṃ deseti. "
msgstr "Now, at that time the Buddha was teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large assembly of laypeople. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.248, sc2
msgctxt "sn4.14:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho mārassa pāpimato etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Māra thought, "

msgctxt "sn4.14:2.2"
msgid "“ayaṃ kho samaṇo gotamo mahatiyā gihiparisāya parivuto dhammaṃ deseti. "
msgstr "“The ascetic Gotama is teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large assembly of laypeople. "

msgctxt "sn4.14:2.3"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkameyyaṃ vicakkhukammāyā”ti. "
msgstr "Why don’t I go and pull the wool over their eyes?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.14:2.4"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and addressed him in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn4.14:3.1"
msgid "“Netaṃ tava patirūpaṃ, "
msgstr "“It’s not appropriate for you "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:3.2"
msgid "yadaññamanusāsasi; "
msgstr "to instruct others. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:3.3"
msgid "Anurodhavirodhesu, "
msgstr "As you engage in this, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:3.4"
msgid "mā sajjittho tadācaran”ti. "
msgstr "don’t get caught up in favoring and opposing.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn4.14:4.1"
msgid "“Hitānukampī sambuddho, "
msgstr "“The Buddha instructs others "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:4.2"
msgid "yadaññamanusāsati; "
msgstr "out of compassion for their welfare. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:4.3"
msgid "Anurodhavirodhehi, "
msgstr "The Realized One is liberated "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.14:4.4"
msgid "vippamutto tathāgato”ti. "
msgstr "from favoring and opposing.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn4.14:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ bhagavā, jānāti maṃ sugato”ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The Buddha knows me! The Holy One knows me!” miserable and sad, vanished right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
